Trust Region Methods

Approximate ff near 𝐱k\mathbf{x}_k using a model function mkm_k
Minimize mkm_k near 𝐱k\mathbf{x}_k by solving minpmk(𝐱k+p)s.t.𝐱k+p∈Trust region
\begin{align}
\min_{p} & m_k\left(\mathbf{x}_k+p\right)\\
\text{s.t.} & \mathbf{x}_k+p \in \text{Trust region}
\end{align}

Common choice: local quadratic Taylor series, with a spherical trust region
(trust-region Newton’s method)

